#: .\construction\furniture.json
msgid ""
"A assembly machine capable of producing BioCo Tech given the correct "
"software."
msgstr "一臺能夠生產BioCo技術的組裝機，前提是擁有正確的軟件。"

#: .\construction\furniture.json
msgid ""
"A BioCo manufacturing device for various chemical components and medicines."
msgstr "一種BioCo製造設備，用於生產各種化學組分和藥物。"

#: .\effects\medicine_effects.json
msgid "XE037 Healing"
msgstr "XE037癒合"

#. ~ Description of effect 'XE037 Healing'.
#: .\effects\medicine_effects.json
msgid "Flesh stiching itself together is never a fun time. Testing."
msgstr "肉體自行縫合從來都不是什麼愉快的體驗。測試中。"

#: .\effects\medicine_effects.json
msgid "XE037 Rapid Healing"
msgstr "XE037快速癒合"

#. ~ Description of effect 'XE037 Rapid Healing'.
#: .\effects\medicine_effects.json
msgid "The ache of your muscles and bones mending temselves grows."
msgstr "肌肉和骨骼自我修復的疼痛感加劇了。"

#: .\effects\medicine_effects.json
msgid "XE037 Cell Breakdown"
msgstr "XE037細胞崩解"

#. ~ Description of effect 'XE037 Cell Breakdown'.
#: .\effects\medicine_effects.json
msgid ""
"Liquified flesh stings as your bone heats. Anymore XE037 is a gamble with "
"death himself."
msgstr "液化的肉體刺痛，骨骼發熱。再使用XE037無異於與死神賭博。"

#: .\effects\medicine_effects.json
msgid "XE037 Rejection"
msgstr "XE037排斥反應"

#. ~ Description of effect 'XE037 Rejection'.
#: .\effects\medicine_effects.json
msgid "Black ooze creeps from your wounds as numbness sets in..."
msgstr "黑色粘液從你的傷口滲出，麻木感隨之而來……"

#. ~ Apply message for effect(s) 'XE037 Healing, XE037 Rapid Healing, XE037
#. Cell Breakdown, XE037 Rejection'.
#: .\effects\medicine_effects.json
msgid ""
"You slam the needle in and begin to feel the sensation of flesh crawling "
"together..."
msgstr "你猛地把針扎進去，開始感覺到肉體蠕動著合攏……"

#. ~ Remove message for effect(s) 'XE037 Healing, XE037 Rapid Healing, XE037
#. Cell Breakdown, XE037 Rejection'.
#: .\effects\medicine_effects.json
msgid "The worst of the healing is over now."
msgstr "最糟糕的癒合階段現在結束了。"

#. ~ Miss message for effect(s) 'XE037 Healing, XE037 Rapid Healing, XE037
#. Cell Breakdown, XE037 Rejection'.
#: .\effects\medicine_effects.json
msgid "A sick squlesh is heard from your insides..."
msgstr "從你體內傳來一陣噁心的擠壓聲……"

#: .\effects\medicine_effects.json
msgid "Nausea Medicine"
msgstr "止吐藥"

#. ~ Description of effect 'Nausea Medicine'.
#: .\effects\medicine_effects.json
msgid "Medicine calms your sotmach and helps prevent vomitting."
msgstr "藥物能安撫你的胃，並有助於防止嘔吐。"

#. ~ Apply message for effect(s) 'Nausea Medicine'.
#: .\effects\medicine_effects.json
msgid "You pop a pill into your mouth. Bitter."
msgstr "你吞下一片藥丸。味道很苦。"

